167
00:14:57,092 --> 00:15:05,741
[SPEAKER_18]: And so I don't know if Will could, so you know firsthand what the kids see.

168
00:15:08,965 --> 00:15:13,447
[SPEAKER_18]: So ST stands for spatial tempora, and so this is all the kids see.

169
00:15:14,048 --> 00:15:21,212
[SPEAKER_18]: So now they have to guess and test what this question is asking them to do.

170
00:15:21,952 --> 00:15:24,654
