178
00:16:08,872 --> 00:16:10,133
[SPEAKER_18]: So that measures the progress.

179
00:16:10,653 --> 00:16:15,335
[SPEAKER_18]: And so the kids over the course of a year are gonna complete over 2,000 puzzles.

180
