240
00:25:10,450 --> 00:25:14,972
[SPEAKER_09]: So Roberts Elementary's last day will be Thursday, June 25th.

241
00:25:15,272 --> 00:25:16,992
[SPEAKER_09]: That will also be a half day.

242
00:25:17,613 --> 00:25:23,335
[SPEAKER_09]: So if you are at the Roberts, your last three days of school will be half days.

243
00:25:25,878 --> 00:25:28,001
[SPEAKER_09]: Are there any questions about that before I move on?

244
00:25:30,243 --> 00:25:30,544
[SPEAKER_09]: Okay.

245
00:25:30,664 --> 00:25:45,202
[SPEAKER_09]: The next part that is tied to the calendar that I just think is important to note, and principals have communicated this in schools that are affected, but because four days fell also within the same grading cycle,

246
