629
01:01:04,867 --> 01:01:20,737
[SPEAKER_00]: It's going to take some time for the architect to give us an initial ranking of those things and then for the committee really to work through, A, that they agree with the relative ranking that has been provided by the architect.

630
01:01:22,678 --> 01:01:27,684
[SPEAKER_00]: sort of digest what that means in terms of like what the options are and how to down select.

631
01:01:27,804 --> 01:01:33,570
[SPEAKER_00]: So the idea is not to rush that down selection so that we can be really thoughtful about how we go forward.

632
01:01:34,611 --> 01:01:41,119
[SPEAKER_00]: Also next week we'll reconvene our advisory committee meetings for meeting number three.

633
01:01:41,139 --> 01:01:42,800
[SPEAKER_00]: And so those are

634
01:01:44,402 --> 01:01:49,784
