636
01:01:52,745 --> 01:01:56,386
[SPEAKER_00]: So we're going to be talking with them about some of their input as we move forward.

637
01:02:10,691 --> 01:02:12,513
[SPEAKER_00]: sort of consideration and thought.

638
01:02:12,633 --> 01:02:20,019
